data.description: Stunning 4-bedroom, 3 full baths in PARKVIEW School District on fully fenced lot bursting with perennials and nestled in conveniently located active swim tennis and playground subdivision!  Features include NEW roof and NEW 6-inch gutters, 3-sides brick, electric vehicle charger, huge slate patio perfect for entertaining and taking in your private, all wooded view!  Living Room or Office plus full bath on main level could double for guest suite!  Spacious Tahoe floor plan with oversized, gourmet granite and stainless Kitchen with upgraded cherry cabinetry, generous center island, double ovens and sunny Breakfast Room with French doors to backyard!  Banquet sized Dining Room, fireside Family Room, and open floor plan makes entertaining family and friends a breeze!  Lovely arched entry doors, wrought iron rails, Butler’s Pantry/Bar, abundant natural light, spacious Laundry Room and hardwoods throughout main level!   Unwind in your Owner’s Suite with Sitting area, trey ceiling, double vanities, relaxing soaking tub, XL shower and oversized walk-in closet and dressing area.  Spacious secondary bedrooms share granite and tile hall bath.  Dramatic loft area ideal for study or play area!   Beautiful patio makes outdoor living and entertaining easy!  Fenced in back yard perfect for kids and pets with no homes behind you to restrict your wooded view!  Conveniently located minutes to award winning schools, beautiful subdivision amenities, restaurants, shops, entertainment, expressways and all that Atlanta has to offer!
